"Airstrikes killed six al Shabaab millitants" - US millitary “A parked car laden with explosives exploded in front of shops. So far we know three people died,” Major Mohamed Hussein, a police officer, told Reuters. “Death toll may rise because there are many shops there.” A Reuters witness saw several destroyed shops and blood stains at the blast scene. 